page.title: 09A day in my life by James L
page.content: I awake at five past eight every morning.I have a wash,get dressed and have my breakfast.Then I clean my teeth,comb my hair,put my lunch into my bag and go to school. When I get to school,I go in or I play football.When the whistle goes,we line up.If we are the first line ready we get a House Point.When I get in I take off my coat and go into the classroom. After I have done my work,the bell rings and we go out to play.When we come back from play we do some maths,then have dinner. In the afternoon we might have art, P.E. or other work.Sometimes we have a fourth year meeting and then we go home. There are 5 pubs in Halling.I live in a pub so I don't get much sleep.
